ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Lab meetings in development psychology with readings from different aread of science that are related to development.I would recommend it to all thouse students interested in development or evolutionary psychology.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The readings and discussions were directly related to the topics studied in the lab, and having the opportunity to present my ideas and get feedback was beneficial.

The knowledge I acquired through this course, not only covers work done in the lab, but also interdisciplinary work related to it. This more global orientation is very important in science. Iprovited a lot from the topics discussed.
